Ghostin' modules:

````typescript
// this pattern has 3 name in top level.
interface NodeFoo {}
interface NodeBar {}
interface NodeBuzz {}

// this pattern has 1 name in top level. Non instantiable module
declare module NodeJS {
    interface Foo {}
    interface Bar {}
    interface Buzz {}
}

// safety!
var n = NodeJS; // TS Error : Could not find symbol NodeJS
````
